Stay Safe Online – Prevention Tips
Do not click on suspicious email links.
Verify website URLs before entering sensitive information.
Use strong, unique passwords for all accounts.
Enable two-factor authentication for online accounts.
Regularly update devices and antivirus software.
Avoid sharing personal or financial details on unknown platforms.
For online payments, double-check UPI/transaction requests before approving.
Do not save payment credentials on public devices.
